templategroup.name: CSS
templategroup.template:
<vb:comment>The header_subtabbar_height stylevar sets this to 45px so the scalloped bottom of the header image shows. This sets the height back to 29px for the text.</vb:comment>
#channel-subtabbar ul li {
	height: 29px;
	line-height: 29px;
}
#channel-subtabbar ul li a {
	line-height: 29px;
}

<vb:comment>/* Fonts used by the Grunge style */</vb:comment>
<vb:comment>/* Capriola */</vb:comment> {vb:template css_font_capriola.css, use_regular=1}
<vb:comment>/* Oswald */</vb:comment> {vb:template css_font_oswald.css, use_regular=1}
